Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.25,0:00:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Then may I have your name and number?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.44,0:00:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Moritaka Mashiro...
