Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.21,0:02:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow? That’s crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess that’s a publisher for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.34,0:02:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.67,0:02:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we’ll be fine if we meet an hour early...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.78,0:02:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How about 1 o’clock, North Yakusa station?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Give or take...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.35,0:02:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.87,0:02:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m— gonna go over the manuscript again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.63,0:02:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let me check the dialogue again too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Where’s Moritaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.51,0:02:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn’t come home yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.82,0:02:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He locked himself in his room as soon as he got home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.93,0:02:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure hope he hasn’t been pushing himself too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.38,0:02:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.67,0:03:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Being a manga artist must be awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.76,0:03:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing your own drawings all lined up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m still just a gambler.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.08,0:03:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Gambler?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.45,0:03:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Manga artists are the ones who can make a living off of only writing manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You either have to hit a jackpot right away
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,or write several fairly successful manga series.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.65,0:03:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest of the folks are all just gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The drawings are good but I don’t know about my story.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The story’s good but I’m not sure about my drawings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.60,0:03:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Our...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,first ever manga...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.41,0:03:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re early!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.68,0:03:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you? Why’re you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.99,0:04:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, despite being sleep deprived, I woke up early.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I just couldn’t lay there doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother said to ask for next week’s Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.83,0:04:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s no way they’d give it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.77,0:04:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Your brother’s at a good university, isn’t he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.23,0:04:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but he kind of gave up since he’s not at his first choice school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now he just parties and does other extracurricular stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.26,0:04:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,making the most of college life, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Not much of a future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So that’s why you wanted to be a manga artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.43,0:04:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I guess ‘cause of my parents, I didn’t want a desk job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad used to be a banker.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.04,0:04:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad’s late today too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.55,0:04:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He’ll be late because of prep school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You had better study hard so you don’t lose to your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes ma’am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how did this semester’s exams go?
