Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.68,0:05:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom taught at a high school, so she made us study every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.88,0:05:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Great job, Akito!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sure your father would be proud too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.69,0:05:19.09,Alt,,0,0,0,,It seems like something got lost in the process of studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do this well on the next ones, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But that’s only in hindsight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.00,0:05:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.19,0:05:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! How is that any different from being fired for your boss’s mistakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What else could I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What else—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, what about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What will become of us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:42.50,Alt,,0,0,0,,Of course, I didn’t really understand what was going at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You got the groceries, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.98,0:05:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother asked me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.03,0:05:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna come with you next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.92,0:05:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure you can, next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:05:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.60,0:06:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then in fifth grade...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.14,0:06:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Avenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
