Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You must...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.00,0:06:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,avenge your father, Akito!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.81,0:06:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What did she mean by “avenge”?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she want me to become the manger of some bank?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.58,0:06:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that why she made me study?
