Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.09,0:18:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s work hard, here at Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything comes up, just send me an email at that address.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t have much time, but I’ll get back to you as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.63,0:18:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn’t be so thrilled about an email address.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.32,0:18:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I’d give out my cell phone number when I find a golden egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.69,0:18:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are still just copper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.73,0:18:36.78,Q_Q,,0,0,0,,Not only did he give us his opinion, he’s joking around with us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.78,0:18:38.57,Q_Q,,0,0,0,,Maybe we can trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.57,0:18:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m gonna submit this for our monthly prize if that’s alright with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.87,0:18:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,By monthly prize, you mean the prize that’s awarded each month to a chosen submission?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.09,0:18:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this going to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.83,0:18:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s not that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.52,0:18:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But people have different tastes,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.04,0:19:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,so maybe some will still consider this as a finalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, we don’t always know what will or won’t be a hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If we did, there wouldn’t be so many new series that end quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.44,0:19:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Predicting what’ll be a hit is pretty much a gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.25,0:19:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest of the folks are all just gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.13,0:19:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give me a call when your next manuscript’s ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.99,0:19:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.08,0:19:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.43,0:19:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a success, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it was our first manuscript, we got an email address...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What’d you think, Shujin?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.93,0:19:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.72,0:19:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Mr. Hattori’s a good editor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.95,0:20:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.57,0:20:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, how’d it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.67,0:20:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,With that middle school pair...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.83,0:20:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Not good enough. At least right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone can’t be a Eiji Nizuma, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.68,0:20:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But he’s only been using a pen for two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The script’s still not quite palatable, but the idea itself is original...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.59,0:20:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So they sparked your interest?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Especially because they’re still just 14.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.32,0:20:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.76,0:20:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Working as a pair isn’t easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.97,0:20:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They’re still kids so they could get in a fight and break up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But since you like them, make sure to raise them well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.33,0:20:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they’ll have surpassed Eiji Nizuma in three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You better pray you have a hit in three years or you’ll be fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.41,0:21:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Any noise annoys an oyster but a noisy noise annoys an oyster most.
