Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.31,0:21:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Unique New York. You know you need unique New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.04,0:21:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sally sells sea shells by the sea shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, summer break ends today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.04,0:21:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And Saiko didn’t hang out with us once!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and I really wanted to see that x-rated one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.24,0:21:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He was hanging out with Takagi the entire break.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.41,0:21:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they were going to prep school together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.05,0:21:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.15,0:21:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna finish another story before the end of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.98,0:21:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And this time he won’t say it should be a light novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.69,0:21:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I’m gonna work on the things he mentioned and make some amazing illustrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.65,0:21:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, the theme of “The Two Earths” was too deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.20,0:21:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A question like ‘What is truth?’ really suits a novel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.38,0:22:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should’ve kept it something more straightforward.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.36,0:22:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So you {\i1}do{\i0} get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.85,0:22:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.22,0:22:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You did? Then you should’ve told me sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.43,0:22:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We agreed I wouldn’t say a word about the names.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.24,0:22:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then next time, say whatever you’re thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.79,0:22:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So let’s put in a lot of time on it and produce something we can both be proud of.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.35,0:22:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If you’re okay with it, then I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.79,0:22:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.42,0:22:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.19,0:22:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how it was when I was in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.39,0:22:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,These are your seats for this trimester.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.43,0:22:44.37,Q_Q,,0,0,0,,What happens if my stomach growls in the middle of class?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.30,0:22:49.64,Songs,,0,0,0,,The boring everyday gets to me sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.30,0:22:49.64,Songs - R,,0,0,0,,Betaa na Genjitsu ni Tsubusaretemo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.64,0:22:55.81,Songs,,0,0,0,,but I always get back on my feet, standing strong
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.64,0:22:55.81,Songs - R,,0,0,0,,Uchinomesareta Jibun Hiroiatsumete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:23:00.56,Songs,,0,0,0,,No matter how many times the end approaches me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:23:00.56,Songs - R,,0,0,0,,Nando Owari ga Otozuretemo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.56,0:23:06.90,Songs,,0,0,0,,I'll push my own back forward, keeping me on my feet
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.56,0:23:06.90,Songs - R,,0,0,0,,Sonotabi ni Jibun de Jibun no Senaka Oshita
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.90,0:23:11.83,Songs,,0,0,0,,If I get lost in the meaning of continuing what I do,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.90,0:23:11.83,Songs - R,,0,0,0,,Tsuzuiteku Imi ni Nayami
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.83,0:23:16.71,Songs,,0,0,0,,I'll rid myself of those worries and keep myself going forward
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.83,0:23:16.71,Songs - R,,0,0,0,,Sono Mayoi Sae Tachikitte Yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.71,0:23:17.87,Songs,,0,0,0,,Always
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.71,0:23:17.87,Songs - R,,0,0,0,,Itsumo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.87,0:23:23.00,Songs,,0,0,0,,The straight edge that draws the outline of my future
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.87,0:23:23.00,Songs - R,,0,0,0,,Mirai no Rinkakusen Kaku Massugu na Jougi wa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.00,0:23:28.68,Songs,,0,0,0,,is made of all the courage I've mustered up until today
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.00,0:23:28.68,Songs - R,,0,0,0,,Ikutsumo no Kinou no Yuuki de Dekiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.68,0:23:33.76,Songs,,0,0,0,,I'll climb over the tall wall that I never thought I'd face,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.68,0:23:33.76,Songs - R,,0,0,0,,Omoiegaita no to Chigau Takai Kabe Koe
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.76,0:23:39.81,Songs,,0,0,0,,and continue my journey, going past the vanishing point
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.76,0:23:39.81,Songs - R,,0,0,0,,Shoushisuten no Mukou e Susunde
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.06,0:23:45.99,Songs,,0,0,0,,This winding road seems to never end,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.06,0:23:45.99,Songs - R,,0,0,0,,Harukanaru Winding Road
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.99,0:23:51.99,Songs,,0,0,0,,but it is the road I personally chose
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.99,0:23:51.99,Songs - R,,0,0,0,,Hoka no Dare Demo Nai Watashi ga Jibun de Eranda
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.99,0:23:59.58,Songs,,0,0,0,,I set my tiny dreams on fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.99,0:23:59.58,Songs - R,,0,0,0,,Kasuka na Yume o Zenbu Moyashita
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.58,0:24:03.79,Songs,,0,0,0,,and broke through the dark with its light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.58,0:24:03.79,Songs - R,,0,0,0,,Sono Hikari de Yami o Saite
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.79,0:24:07.84,Songs,,0,0,0,,Now that I've broken down the wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.79,0:24:07.84,Songs - R,,0,0,0,,Kudaita Kabe no Mukou ni
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.84,0:24:13.30,Songs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1500)}I can see my sky once more
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.84,0:24:13.30,Songs - R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1500)}Jibun no Sora ga Mieru
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.26,0:24:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,An editor gave us his contact information, and now I sit next to Azuki.
