Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.15,0:24:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything’s going smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.76,0:24:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And our rival’s made his move.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.88,0:24:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.83,0:24:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, Tears and More Tears.
